         MACRO                                                                  
&L       TREND &TYPE                                                            
.*  Added 3/83, Niz                                                             
&L       LABEL                                                                  
         AIF   ('&TYPE' EQ '').CALL                                             
         LA    R15,TTY&TYPE-TTYPE                                               
.CALL    VCALL TREND                                                            
         MEND                                                                   
